  72:src/voice.h   ****   // repeats allowed; LARGER = slower. 0 = off (only a full lift + re-tap
  73:src/voice.h   ****   // retriggers). A full lift always retriggers regardless. Default 0 keeps the
  74:src/voice.h   ****   // melodic voices free of accidental re-articulation; drums set a value.
