 640:src/voice.h   **** // ŌöĆŌöĆ Voice 9: kick drum (noise-driven) ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌ
 641:src/voice.h   **** //   A deep, punchy thud ŌĆö PLAY IT BY TAPPING. A low sine body with a sub-octave
 642:src/voice.h   **** //   for weight and a quiet octave "click" for beater attack; a whisper of noise
 643:src/voice.h   **** //   adds beater texture. Very closed dark filter + a little drive keep it round
 644:src/voice.h   **** //   and punchy. Instant attack, short tail. Finger-1 position tunes the kick.
 645:src/voice.h   **** //   A pitch envelope (start 2 oct up, drop in 45 ms) gives the classic "boom".
 646:src/voice.h   **** static constexpr Voice VOICE_KICK = {
 647:src/voice.h   ****     "Kick",
